text: Husák or Husak is a surname which may refer to: * Emil J. Husak (born 1930), American politician * Gustáv Husák (1913–1991), Slovak politician, president of Czechoslovakia and a long-term General Secretary of the Communist Party of Czechoslovakia * Patrik Husák (born 1990), Czech ice hockey player * Todd Husak (born 1978), American football quarterback * Walter J. Husak (born 1942), American coin collector and business owner ==See also== *
title: Husák
